<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= typeof pageTitle !== 'undefined' ? pageTitle : 'Quên mật khẩu' %></title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Sora:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-top: #eff7ff;
      --bg-mid: #f8fbff;
      --bg-bottom: #ffe8f1;
      --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      --panel-edge: rgba(110, 143, 204, 0.14);
      --field: rgba(248, 251, 255, 0.98);
      --field-edge: rgba(110, 143, 204, 0.14);
      --text: #17314c;
      --muted: #667c96;
      --muted-strong: #44607e;
      --accent-start: #ff7a59;
      --accent-mid: #ff5d8f;
      --accent-end: #ffb14a;
      --accent-text: #ffffff;
      --line: rgba(110, 143, 204, 0.14);
      --success: #067647;
      --danger: #b42318;
      --info: #175cd3;
      --shadow: 0 36px 90px rgba(44, 78, 129, 0.14);
      --brand: #2f78ed;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      min-height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Manrope", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.16), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255, 93, 143, 0.14), transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(255, 177, 74, 0.16), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, var(--bg-top) 0%, var(--bg-mid) 42%, var(--bg-bottom) 100%);
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(110, 143, 204, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(110, 143, 204, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
      opacity: 0.34;
      pointer-events: none;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black, transparent 88%);
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    button,
    input {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .recovery-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 34px 22px 48px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .recovery-shell {
      width: min(100%, 1160px);
      margin: 0 auto;
      flex: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 28px;
      align-content: start;
    }

    .recovery-brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      width: fit-content;
      margin-left: 6px;
    }

    .recovery-brand-mark {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.14) 0%, rgba(255, 93, 143, 0.18) 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.14);
    }

    .recovery-brand-mark img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      padding: 4px;
      display: block;
    }

    .recovery-brand-copy {
      font-family: "Sora", "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-start) 0%, var(--accent-mid) 48%, var(--accent-end) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .recovery-stage {
      display: grid;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .recovery-card {
      width: min(100%, 760px);
      padding: 40px 34px 34px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96) 0%, rgba(251, 253, 255, 0.98) 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-edge);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .recovery-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -20% auto auto -18%;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.12), transparent 72%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .recovery-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -14% -16% auto;
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 93, 143, 0.14), transparent 72%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .recovery-stack {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .recovery-copy {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .recovery-overline {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.08);
      color: var(--brand);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .recovery-copy h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Sora", "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-start) 0%, var(--accent-mid) 48%, var(--accent-end) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .recovery-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .recovery-flash-stack,
    .recovery-tips {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .recovery-flash,
    .recovery-tip {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 0.97rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
    }

    .recovery-flash.success {
      color: var(--success);
      background: rgba(236, 253, 243, 0.96);
      border-color: rgba(6, 118, 71, 0.14);
    }

    .recovery-flash.error {
      color: var(--danger);
      background: rgba(254, 243, 242, 0.96);
      border-color: rgba(180, 35, 24, 0.14);
    }

    .recovery-flash.info,
    .recovery-tip.info {
      color: var(--info);
      background: rgba(239, 248, 255, 0.96);
      border-color: rgba(23, 92, 211, 0.14);
    }

    .recovery-form {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .recovery-label {
      color: var(--muted-strong);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .recovery-input-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 28px minmax(0, 1fr);
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      min-height: 76px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: var(--field);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--field-edge);
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .recovery-input-wrap:focus-within {
      border-color: rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.28);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.2), 0 18px 34px rgba(44, 78, 129, 0.12);
    }

    .recovery-input-icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #557190;
    }

    .recovery-input {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 0;
      border: 0;
      outline: none;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 1.04rem;
    }

    .recovery-input::placeholder {
      color: rgba(102, 124, 150, 0.58);
    }

    .recovery-submit {
      min-height: 72px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-start) 0%, var(--accent-mid) 48%, var(--accent-end) 100%);
      color: var(--accent-text);
      font-family: "Sora", "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 46px rgba(255, 93, 143, 0.24);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .recovery-submit:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 28px 52px rgba(255, 93, 143, 0.3);
    }

    .recovery-steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .recovery-step {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
      border: 1px solid rgba(110, 143, 204, 0.12);
    }

    .recovery-step-badge {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: rgba(47, 120, 237, 0.1);
      color: var(--brand);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .recovery-step h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .recovery-step p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .recovery-footer {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .recovery-footer a {
      color: var(--brand);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .recovery-steps {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .recovery-page {
        padding: 28px 14px 40px;
      }

      .recovery-card {
        padding: 32px 22px 24px;
        border-radius: 32px;
      }

      .recovery-input-wrap {
        min-height: 70px;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%
    const safeBaseUrl = typeof baseUrl !== 'undefined' ? baseUrl : '';
    const safeSuccessMessages = typeof success_msg !== 'undefined' ? success_msg : [];
    const safeErrorMessages = typeof error_msg !== 'undefined' ? error_msg : [];
    const safeInfoMessages = typeof info !== 'undefined' ? info : [];
    const emailValue = typeof formEmail !== 'undefined' ? formEmail : '';
    const smtpReady = Boolean(typeof mailConfigured !== 'undefined' ? mailConfigured : false);
    const brandLogo = 'https://i.postimg.cc/P5r5F9Mt/logo.jpg';
  %>

  <main class="recovery-page">
    <div class="recovery-shell">
      <a href="<%= safeBaseUrl %>/" class="recovery-brand" aria-label="Về trang chủ">
        <span class="recovery-brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="<%= brandLogo %>" alt="Logo Thầy Tài Toeic">
        </span>
        <span class="recovery-brand-copy">THAYTAI</span>
      </a>

      <section class="recovery-stage">
        <div class="recovery-card">
          <div class="recovery-stack">
            <div class="recovery-copy">
              <span class="recovery-overline">Khôi phục truy cập</span>
              <h1>Quên mật khẩu?</h1>
              <p>Nhập email đã dùng để đăng nhập. Hệ thống sẽ gửi cho bạn một liên kết đặt lại mật khẩu an toàn để bạn quay lại tài khoản nhanh chóng.</p>
            </div>

            <% if (safeSuccessMessages.length || safeErrorMessages.length || safeInfoMessages.length) { %>
              <div class="recovery-flash-stack">
                <% safeSuccessMessages.forEach((msg) => { %>
                  <div class="recovery-flash success"><%= msg %></div>
                <% }) %>
                <% safeErrorMessages.forEach((msg) => { %>
                  <div class="recovery-flash error"><%= msg %></div>
                <% }) %>
                <% safeInfoMessages.forEach((msg) => { %>
                  <div class="recovery-flash info"><%= msg %></div>
                <% }) %>
              </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="recovery-tips">
              <div class="recovery-tip info">
                Nếu bạn đăng nhập bằng Google hoặc Facebook, bạn nên dùng lại nút đăng nhập tương ứng ở trang đăng nhập thay vì đặt lại mật khẩu.
              </div>
              <% if (!smtpReady) { %>
                <div class="recovery-tip info">
                  Kênh gửi email khôi phục hiện chưa được cấu hình đầy đủ. Bạn vẫn có thể mở luồng này, nhưng để nhận mail thật cần bật SMTP trong hệ thống.
                </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>

            <form action="<%= safeBaseUrl %>/forgot-password" method="POST" class="recovery-form">
              <label class="recovery-label" for="forgotEmail">Gmail / Email đăng nhập</label>
              <label class="recovery-input-wrap" for="forgotEmail">
                <span class="recovery-input-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M4 6h16v12H4z"></path>
                    <path d="m4 7 8 6 8-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <input class="recovery-input" id="forgotEmail" type="email" name="email" placeholder="name@gmail.com" autocomplete="email" required value="<%= emailValue %>">
              </label>

              <button class="recovery-submit" type="submit">Gửi liên kết đặt lại</button>
            </form>

            <div class="recovery-steps" aria-label="Các bước khôi phục mật khẩu">
              <article class="recovery-step">
                <div class="recovery-step-badge">1</div>
                <h2>Nhập đúng email</h2>
                <p>Dùng email bạn đã đăng ký để hệ thống tìm đúng tài khoản và chuẩn bị liên kết đặt lại.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="recovery-step">
                <div class="recovery-step-badge">2</div>
                <h2>Mở email nhận link</h2>
                <p>Kiểm tra hộp thư đến hoặc thư rác. Liên kết được gửi riêng cho bạn và chỉ có hiệu lực trong thời gian ngắn.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="recovery-step">
                <div class="recovery-step-badge">3</div>
                <h2>Đặt mật khẩu mới</h2>
                <p>Tạo mật khẩu mới để đăng nhập lại ngay, sau đó quay về khu học viên hoặc lớp học của mình.</p>
              </article>
            </div>

            <div class="recovery-footer">
              <span>Nhớ lại mật khẩu rồi? <a href="<%= safeBaseUrl %>/login">Quay lại đăng nhập</a></span>
              <span>Cần người hỗ trợ? <a href="<%= safeBaseUrl %>/contact">Liên hệ trung tâm</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
